Source: I002 and `docs/superpowers/plans/2026-07-17-profile-refresh-transaction.md`, Task 2.

Implement pure `ProfileRefresh.run(input, ports, emit)` plus deterministic mock credential/HTTP/cache/clock ports. Own started/credential/terminal transitions, stable identity/generation, once-only settlement, auth state, 429 backoff, timeout classification, and provider aggregation.

Acceptance: mock tests cover busy and valid credential reads, non-zero exit with valid stdout, missing/malformed auth, token rotation/manual retry, auth suspension, backoff ceiling, duplicate callbacks, cache-once, Grok ordering/partial success, and no input mutation.